SCHEMA: appshell/log_category_registry.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.appshell.log_category_registry
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define the registry of canonical AppShell log categories.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record log_category_registry
  required:
    - schema_version: tag
    - registry_id: id
    - categories: [record]
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- category ids must be unique
- category ordering must be deterministic
